text: Contoderopsis aurivillii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1956.Biolib.cz - Contoderopsis aurivillii. Retrieved September 8, 2014. It is endemic to the Philippines. ==References== Category:Acanthocinini Category:Beetles described in 1956 Category:Endemic fauna of the Philippines Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
title: Contoderopsis aurivillii
